  <brief_title>A Multi-Center, Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel Group Study With 3 Groups Receiving Placebo, 5 mg of E2020 and 10 mg of E2020</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Eisai Limited</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Eisai Inc.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the dose-response efficacy of E2020 (5 mg/day and 10 mg/day) versus placebo and
      verify superiority of E2020 to placebo in patients with severe AD using CIBIC-plus* and SIB**
      as the primary efficacy measures. Safety of E2020 will also be evaluated.

      (*for overall evalution of clinical symtoms) (**for cognitive function test)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
